🚨 𝐁𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐈𝐍𝐆: Real Madrid-Bournemouth have reached club to club agreement for Dean Huijsen, £50m clause to be paid by end of 2027 ⚪️🏁

Final green light still needed to proceed seal the deal with player’s camp after contract sent earlier today as Huijsen always gave priority to his Real Madrid dream.

…𝐚𝐥𝐦𝐨𝐬𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞. More to follow. ⏳🇪🇸
